{"tid":467778,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【巴塞隆拿亞洲電影節】惠英紅《幸運是我》揚威海外 獲最佳女演員獎","createTime":"2017-11-13T21:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T11:26:32.000Z","uid":14730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1226b531f11bcf52159234962cc64d79a09361e1","tid":467778,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T21:01:20.000Z","msg":"惠英紅今年4月憑《幸運是我》奪得香港電影金像獎影后寶座後，今天（11月13日）再憑同一部電影於巴塞隆拿亞洲電影節獲最佳女演員獎，是次得獎不但為港爭光，更為紅姐的演技給了一個國際性的肯定。<br />\n<br />\n本年度參與巴塞隆拿亞洲電影節的電影超過一百部，要在當中脫穎而出實在不簡單。平心而論，紅姐在《幸運是我》演繹的腦退化症患者絕對超班，而電影講述獨居老人與被遺棄的年青人由不相識到互相照顧的過程班實扣人心弦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2zSaH1T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2zSaH1T&d=4YZ4Yc6MFKezhAiTN64FIIsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=84d73db9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2zSaH1T</a>"},{"pid":"dea1fe43d4571ac2980d1e56fab2c47e760d99a1","tid":467778,"uid":38293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T21:02:39.000Z","msg":"紅姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f483d2b1188142591683164f4b477edeadde0627","tid":467778,"uid":15935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T21:02:58.000Z","msg":"佢真係拎好多獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8eb6e68411c1663d32b3c2d26326fead43efcf","tid":467778,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T21:06:28.000Z","msg":"學某啲連登會員話齋，票房差，垃圾"},{"pid":"8e0c84dbb831a453ea671bc7e5edace4954bae9b","tid":467778,"uid":37237,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T21:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/14/051546_e50040f07d9a96ca7ff0870bc412a145.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F14%2F051546_e50040f07d9a96ca7ff0870bc412a145.jpg&h=0bf38b91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7cc31b8290c5038b6597be10f23cc6b4e6754474","tid":